      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should probably see someone but i'm super busy with work right now and an appointment is gonna take forever. the drops aren't even that old, they were just opened a few months ago. do you really think it's that serious if it's just redness and some discharge? it feels like i just need to hydrate my eyes because of the screen time. if i just use the drops a few times a day, it should be fine right?",
